title: #92Noon Friday Feast with Larry Michael, Alex Stalock, and Josh Berhow!
description: The show is live from the TCO Performance Center in Eagan for the Friday Football Feast! Paul, Paul, and Nordo talk to Redskins play-by-play announcer Larry Michael, Wild goaltender Alex Stalock, and Golf.com’s Josh Berhow.
